Investment company Appropriate Balance Financial Services Inc. buys Vanguard Growth ETF - DNQ, Amazon.com Inc, Tesla Inc, sells PayPal Holdings Inc during the 3-months ended 2017-06-30, according to the most recent filings of the investment company, Appropriate Balance Financial Services Inc.. As of 2017-06-30, Appropriate Balance Financial Services Inc. owns 28 stocks with a total value of $2 billion.  These are the details of the buys and sells.New Purchases: AMZN, Added Positions: XLF, XLI, VEA, VTV, VUG, VO, VWO, SPY, TSLA, MSFT, Reduced Positions: IVE, QQQ, DIS, Sold Out: PYPL, 
