7-06-30. Sold Out: PayPal Holdings Inc (PYPL)Appropriate Balance Financial Services Inc. sold out the holdings in  PayPal Holdings Inc.  The sale prices were between $42.49 and $54.39, with an estimated average price of $48.98. Here is the complete portfolio of APPROPRIATE BALANCE FINANCIAL SERVICES INC.. Also check out:
