Overview







Description
        
Appropriate Balance Financial Services Inc is an RIA based in Bellevue, WA with $361M in AUM and 9 advisors nationwide.

Appropriate Balance helps people find financial peace of mind freeing them to spend more time with family, community, and personal interests, enjoying their lives to the fullest. 

ABFS was foundedRead More in 1984 with a focus on serving physicians across the country. Many of those clients are still with us over 20 years later. Today our focus has grown to include the broader health care community. We also serve many clients with different backgrounds as well. 

In addition to clients, many of our advisors and staff have been with ABFS for 10+ years, because we all share the same philosophy of caring for and serving the client; and the same values of honesty, integrity, dependability, trustworthiness and offering quality advice focused on the client’s needs. 

The basis of our work is developing meaningful financial relationships with our clients through comprehensive personal financial planning, investment & risk management, and retirement & pension planning. We can work with other professionals that you have a relationship with or we can introduce you to our network. 

Our commitment is to provide honest and ethical wealth management services that help you reach your financial goals and attain financial peace of mind.Read Less











